Preconditions:
- The lengths of the `tops` and `bottoms` arrays are equal.
- The lengths of the `tops` and `bottoms` arrays are at least 2.
- The values in the `tops` and `bottoms` arrays are between 1 and 6 (inclusive).

Postconditions:
- The method returns an integer value.
- If it is possible to make all the values in the `tops` array the same or all the values in the `bottoms` array the same, the method returns the minimum number of rotations required.
- If it is not possible to make all the values in the `tops` array the same or all the values in the `bottoms` array the same, the method returns -1.